meetupr: Access Meetup Data

Source: R/meetupr-package.R
meetupr-package.Rd

Provides programmatic access to the 'Meetup' GraphQL API (https://www.meetup.com/api/schema/), enabling users to retrieve information about groups, events, and members from 'Meetup' (https://www.meetup.com/). Supports authentication via 'OAuth2' and includes functions for common queries and data manipulation tasks.
